Synopsis:           Numeric Linear Algebra
Description:        Linear algebra based on BLAS and LAPACK.
Category:           Math
tested-with:        GHC==7.8

cabal-version:      >=1.8

build-type:         Simple

extra-source-files: THANKS.md CHANGELOG

